  "api": "FireHydrant API v1 (https://firehydrant.com/docs/api/)",
  "docs": "https://firehydrant.com/docs/api/",
  "reviewed_at": "2026-07-03",
  "scope": "wave2 fan-out migration: the 5 legacy-parity read streams only (incidents, services, teams, environments, functionalities); the full FireHydrant surface (retrospectives, runbooks, tasks, changes, alerts, on-call schedules, etc.) is out of scope until Pass B. firehydrant has no allow-listed write actions in legacy (read-only connector).",
